# Learnings Inbox

Sessions across all projects drop durable learnings here as `<epoch-seconds>.md`
(rule defined in `home/ai/3-rules.md` section 17).

Sessions running inside this repo consolidate the queue into the right `home/ai/*`
or `home/claude/*` files (rule defined in this repo's `CLAUDE.md` -> "Learnings Ingestion"),
then move processed files to `processed/`.

The `*.md` content is gitignored — only this README is checked in so the directory persists.
